OL,3,CMore than 10,000 drivers handed
OL,4,Cpenalty points for unroadworthy
OL,5,Cvehicles in 2025
OL,7,FMore than 10,000 drivers in Britain
OL,8,Fwere caught driving unroadworthy
OL,9,Fvehicles last year, an investigation
OL,10,Fhas found.
OL,12,FThe RAC, which obtained the Driver and
OL,13,FVehicle Licensing Agency (DVLA)
OL,14,Ffigures, warned that "far too many
OL,15,Fvehicles are unfit for the roads".
OL,17,FSome 10,054 motorists were handed
OL,18,Fpenalty points in 2025 for driving
OL,19,Fvehicles with problems such as
OL,20,Fdefective brakes, tyres or steering.
OL,26,@vD@VOUwD@aO]
