OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782776882
OL,3,CMore than 10,000 drivers handed
OL,4,Cpenalty points for unroadworthy
OL,5,Cvehicles in 2025
OL,7,FThis was a reduction of 3,055 from the
OL,8,Fprevious year, but the RAC claimed it
OL,9,Fis "hard to know" whether this was
OL,10,Fbecause of improved vehicle
OL,11,Fmaintenance or fewer traffic officers
OL,12,Fon the roads.
OL,14,FThe part of Britain with the most
OL,15,Fdrivers of unroadworthy vehicles
OL,16,Fcaught in 2025 was Scotland, with
OL,17,F1,244.
OL,19,FIt was followed by London (1,182),
OL,20,FYorkshire and the Humber (995) and the
OL,21,FWest Midlands (969).
OL,26,@qD@DOUqD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
