OL,3,CMore than 10,000 drivers handed
OL,4,Cpenalty points for unroadworthy
OL,5,Cvehicles in 2025
OL,7,FMost cases of driving an unroadworthy
OL,8,Fvehicle result in three penalty points
OL,9,Fbeing issued, which stay on licences
OL,10,Ffor four years.
OL,12,FRAC mechanic of the year Jack Halstead
OL,13,Fsaid: "Far too many vehicles are unfit
OL,14,Ffor the roads, posing a danger not
OL,15,Fonly to the driver, but to other road
OL,16,Fusers as well.
OL,18,F"Having bald tyres drastically reduces
OL,19,Fgrip, greatly increases stopping
OL,20,Fdistances, and raises the risk of
OL,21,Fblowouts.
OL,26,@uD@GOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
