PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782776882
OL,3,CMore than 10,000 drivers handed
OL,4,Cpenalty points for unroadworthy
OL,5,Cvehicles in 2025
OL,7,F"But whether it's tyres, brakes,
OL,8,Fsteering or something else, every
OL,9,Fmechanical component in a vehicle
OL,10,Fplays a critical role.
OL,12,F"And this is likely to be just the tip
OL,13,Fof the iceberg; with fewer police
OL,14,Ftraffic units, it's likely more
OL,15,Foffenders are evading officers and
OL,16,Fputting themselves and others at risk."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@gO]
